caption.p: 2nd cycles of cyclic voltammograms recorded at a 5 mm diameter glassy carbon disk electrode at 50 mV/s of ( A) [V(acac) 3] (10 mM) in [emim][NTf 2], ( B) [V(acac) 3] (11 mM) in [bmim][BF 4] ( C) [V(acac) 3] (12 mM) in [bmim][PF 6], ( D) [V(acac) 3] (12 mM) in [emim][N(CN) 2] and ( E) [V(acac) 3] (20 mM) in [emim][EtSO 4]. All cyclic voltammograms began at the negative potential limit. Reproduced with permission from [ 42], copyright 2020, Springer.
